com.linkly.pos.sdk.models.display

Class DisplayResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.linkly.pos.sdk.models.PosApiResponse
      • com.linkly.pos.sdk.models.display.DisplayResponse

  • public class DisplayResponse
extends PosApiResponse
    This message is returned asynchronously when a display event occurs on the PIN pad. To handle display events refer to IPosApiEventListener.display(java.util.UUID, com.linkly.pos.sdk.models.PosApiRequest, DisplayResponse)
